    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition \u2014 a used car that remains functional and drivable but shows its age and history more noticeably than a good or mint example. The exterior displays visible wear including scattered scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents or dings that are apparent upon close inspection. The interior is serviceable but shows clear signs of use, with worn upholstery, scuffed trim pieces, and some areas that could benefit from cleaning or minor repair. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though prospective buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term to keep it operating reliably. This is a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind putting a little work into a vehicle or accepting cosmetic imperfections in exchange for a lower price point.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what to expect. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains most of its original depth and color, with only minor blemishes, light surface scratches, and small imperfections consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or rust concerns. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces that you'd expect from a well-used vehicle, but nothing that detracts from daily comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately; however, as with any pre-owned vehicle in this condition tier, a pre-purchase inspection is always recommended to confirm your comfort level. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are in working order. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that offers good value for a buyer looking for reliable transportation without paying a premium for showroom-perfect condition.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 a designation we reserve exclusively for cars that genuinely earn it, and this one does so without reservation. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains its original depth and luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels align perfectly with consistent, tight gaps throughout. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 every surface is clean and unmarked, the upholstery shows no wear, and all electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, with full service records available to document its care. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires nothing \u2014 simply drive and enjoy. Buyers seeking a truly exceptional, move-in-ready car will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 45000.0,
